591
00:25:48,416 --> 00:25:49,756 A:middle
And then further in the game,

592
00:25:50,426 --> 00:25:53,096 A:middle
they start showing you
advanced obstacles or puzzles.

593
00:25:53,186 --> 00:25:57,626 A:middle
So you can see how the
complexity builds up that way.

594
00:25:57,846 --> 00:25:59,606 A:middle
Now like I said, the
same thing applies

595
00:25:59,666 --> 00:26:01,236 A:middle
to apps, it's not just games.

596

