00:29:16,446 --> 00:29:20,336 A:middle
So if you do need onboarding,

671
00:29:20,936 --> 00:29:23,436 A:middle
make sure that your experience
lets people participate.

672
00:29:23,436 --> 00:29:28,766 A:middle
And you can use animation
to do a lot of teaching.

673
00:29:28,886 --> 00:29:30,376 A:middle
It's a really powerful tool.

