00:34:27,835 --> 00:34:29,426 A:middle
about when it comes
to writing your text.

787
00:34:30,295 --> 00:34:31,906 A:middle
Ask yourself these questions.

788
00:34:32,906 --> 00:34:35,696 A:middle
Could the text be shorter
or could it be clearer?

789
00:34:36,065 --> 00:34:39,396 A:middle
Will the text make sense
to someone who's new

790
00:34:39,396 --> 00:34:43,025 A:middle
to the application, because
you look at your app all day

791
00:34:43,025 --> 00:34:47,116 A:middle
and all night every day, so you
really need fresh perspective,

792
00:34:47,116 --> 00:34:50,136 A:middle
and what will someone
unfamiliar with your app think?

793
00:34:50,616 --> 00:34:53,866 A:middle
Is the message too complicated?

794
00:34:54,315 --> 00:34:58,596 A:middle
If it is, you can make it
simpler, or maybe you need

795
00:34:58,596 --> 00:35:00,276 A:middle
to change your approach
altogether.

