1180
00:51:57,916 --> 00:52:00,356 A:middle
Oh, I didn't have
my phone number yet.

1181
00:52:00,946 --> 00:52:04,376 A:middle
Shoot. And what's the
star mean, I wonder?

1182
00:52:05,086 --> 00:52:06,126 A:middle
