1185
00:52:12,806 --> 00:52:15,536 A:middle
They're just letting you know
about commenting because that's

1186
00:52:15,536 --> 00:52:16,736 A:middle
where you are in the app.

1187
00:52:17,506 --> 00:52:19,206 A:middle
