1228
00:53:59,416 --> 00:54:02,416 A:middle
And that's why with Siri, we
give you a lot of suggestions

1229
00:54:02,416 --> 00:54:03,956 A:middle
of things that you can ask her.

1230
00:54:04,056 --> 00:54:06,546 A:middle
You just tap that question
mark button and you're going

1231
00:54:06,546 --> 00:54:09,456 A:middle
to get a long list of things
that you can ask Siri.

1232
00:54:10,246 --> 00:54:13,756 A:middle
And you may have known that you
can use Siri to initiate calls

1233
00:54:13,756 --> 00:54:17,056 A:middle
or have her make an
appointment on your calendar,

1234
00:54:17,056 --> 00:54:20,216 A:middle
but did you know that she also
will book restaurants for you

1235
00:54:20,776 --> 00:54:22,086 A:middle
or tell you movie times?

1236
00:54:22,336 --> 00:54:25,036 A:middle
I mean, this list goes
on, and on and on.

1237
00:54:27,076 --> 00:54:29,376 A:middle
"Path" does it with some
of their onboarding.

1238
00:54:29,836 --> 00:54:32,956 A:middle
And they're a private social
network, so they really need you

1239
00:54:32,956 --> 00:54:35,086 A:middle
to register because
everything is oriented

1240
00:54:35,086 --> 00:54:36,436 A:middle
around your personal
information.

1241
00:54:37,436 --> 00:54:40,736 A:middle
But before registering, they're
giving you a series of screens

1242
00:54:40,736 --> 00:54:44,176 A:middle
that covers both the
features of the apps

1243
00:54:44,316 --> 00:54:46,886 A:middle
but also how you might
want to use them.

1244
00:54:48,286 --> 00:54:50,616 A:middle
A lot of people go to "Path"
thinking they're going to use it

1245
00:54:50,616 --> 00:54:52,456 A:middle
for work, but now, they're
going to be thinking

1246
00:54:52,456 --> 00:54:55,226 A:middle
about how they can use it
in their personal life, too.

1247
00:54:57,516 --> 00:55:01,096 A:middle
Or with Pinterest, they've
got a similar approach.

1248

1249
