1250
00:54:57,516 --> 00:55:01,096 A:middle
Or with Pinterest, they've
got a similar approach.

1251
00:55:01,696 --> 00:55:03,236 A:middle
I mean, maybe you
came to Pinterest

1252
00:55:03,236 --> 00:55:06,296 A:middle
because you were interested
in nail art or wanting recipes

1253
00:55:06,296 --> 00:55:08,706 A:middle
for a dinner party, but
now you're also thinking

1254
00:55:08,706 --> 00:55:09,806 A:middle
about gardening.

1255
00:55:10,806 --> 00:55:11,716 A:middle
And then you're thinking

1256
00:55:11,716 --> 00:55:13,846 A:middle
about what else Pinterest
can be used for.

1257
00:55:14,496 --> 00:55:19,106 A:middle
So step away from that
traditional idea of help,

1258
00:55:19,586 --> 00:55:22,006 A:middle
reference manuals, and think

1259
00:55:22,006 --> 00:55:24,366 A:middle
about how you can
anticipate people's needs.

1260
00:55:25,506 --> 00:55:27,726 A:middle
Putting instructions
in empty containers

1261
00:55:27,726 --> 00:55:30,186 A:middle
and showing supporting
information inline,

1262
00:55:30,706 --> 00:55:33,446 A:middle
it's about telling people what
they need to know in that moment

1263
00:55:33,966 --> 00:55:37,036 A:middle
that they need to know it
- like the perfect service

1264
00:55:37,096 --> 00:55:39,976 A:middle
in a restaurant, there
when you need them

1265
00:55:39,976 --> 00:55:42,956 A:middle
and invisible when you don't.

1266
00:55:43,066 --> 00:55:45,006 A:middle
When you're doing all
of that, don't forget

1267
00:55:45,036 --> 00:55:47,166 A:middle
to take the opportunity
to inspire people,

1268
00:55:47,166 --> 00:55:49,056 A:middle
because that increased
knowledge,

1269
00:55:49,316 --> 00:55:51,286 A:middle
that increased utility
about your app,

1270
00:55:51,286 --> 00:55:53,566 A:middle
it's going to mean
increased value.

1271
00:55:54,376 --> 00:55:59,386 A:middle
So if you only take a few things
away from this talk today,

1272
00:55:59,546 --> 00:56:04,426 A:middle
in summary, only require
people to register

1273

1274
