1280
00:56:16,016 --> 00:56:17,496 A:middle
tell them what they need
to know and then get

1281
00:56:17,496 --> 00:56:18,536 A:middle
out of the way quickly.

1282
00:56:19,766 --> 00:56:21,836 A:middle
Teach through actions
because people are going

1283
00:56:21,836 --> 00:56:23,066 A:middle
to learn better by doing.

1284
00:56:24,816 --> 00:56:28,306 A:middle
Anticipate people's
needs, and don't forget

1285
00:56:28,306 --> 00:56:30,046 A:middle
to take the opportunity
to inspire.

1286
00:56:31,206 --> 00:56:34,256 A:middle
Now, I hope that you'll leave
